# STEP 5 – Country Selection

Review how country selection currently works.

Improve it.

Requirements:

* first launch asks for country
* remember selected country
* allow changing later
* automatically adjust

  * language
  * date format
  * measurement units
  * currency
  * timezone
  * business rules
  * phone formatting
  * regional settings

Support future expansion.

Current target markets include GCC countries but architecture must support global deployment.

