# STEP 6 – Professional Onboarding Wizard

Create a complete onboarding wizard.

First-time users should never feel lost.

The onboarding must explain:

What Tyre Pulse is.

How inspections work.

How syncing works.

Offline mode.

Photo capture.

Drafts.

Inspection submission.

Pending sync.

Completed inspections.

Navigation.

Notifications.

Safety reminders.

Role-specific responsibilities.

The onboarding should adapt to user role.

Example:

Tyre Man sees Tyre Man onboarding.

Fleet Manager sees Fleet Manager onboarding.

Workshop Staff sees Workshop onboarding.

The onboarding should be skippable and replayable later.

Include:

illustrations

animations

progress indicator

tips

checklists

interactive walkthroughs

